p: The levels of various molecules were detectable in the serum samples, but only the levels of cytokines IL-1RA, IL-12p40, IL-7, IL-17a, IL-13, EGF, VEGF and CCL11 ( Fig 5Aâ€“5G) showed differences between the serum of patients infected with the L1 lineage and those infected with the L6 lineage. Whereas the levels of IL-12p40, IL-7, IL-17a and VEGF were elevated in patients infected with L1, the levels of IL-1RA, IL-13, EGF and CCL11 were greater in patients infected with L6. None of the other tested molecules showed significant differences ( S3 Fig).
